## ğŸ“Œ 1. Overview

This is a PHP-based **online learning and productivity platform** developed as a group project.  
It includes modules for learning, quizzes, to-do tasks, authentication, admin management, and a simple chatbot.  
The project also includes **Docker support** and **CI/CD folder structure**, making it deployment-ready.

